1)bind => nea metabliti (pseuto nea,giati tin timi tous tin parago apo kapia idi iparxon me clojure kodika)

  Ta bind mpenoun ston pinaka mono ean(alios antikatastasi os pros tis metablites ton trees)
  1)xrisimopoiounte se pola simia H poli argi function
    *mpori o xristis na lei :save  (?var (argi_function ....) :save)
     se auti tin periptosi den thelo na ta ipologizo se pola simia xana kai xana
  2)iparxoun sto project
    (automata to :save to bazi to programa oxi o xristis)

2)2 periptosis

  1)bind iparxi sto project
    thelo tin timi tou


  2)bind den iparxi sto project
    tha mporousa na ta exafaniso ,alla thelo na mioso tous ipologismous
    ara kai pali ta kratao

  Pote efarmozo to bind?
  oso pio noris exo tis metablites pou xriazome

3)ta bind ta kratao se xexoristo pinaka alla me to idio line-id
  i sto idio?

4)otan xekinao prepei na bro mia seira exartisis ton binds

  proto = exartate mono apo relation metablites
  deutero = exartate max apo to proto
  trito = exartate apo to deuteo/proto
  ktl

2)opos kai sta filtra mpori na einai

  single bind
  tree bind
  trees bind
  singles+trees bind

3)Pote to efarmozo
  tautoxrona me tin teleutea metabliti pou xriazonte
  kai tautoxrona i pio meta filtra pou xrisimopioun tin bind metabliti

3)mporo na bro pies einai oi bind metablites giati den simetexoun stis relation queries

4)Mpori na exo pola binds,osa den zitounte sto project,feugoun kai ginete antikatastasi
  me aplo clojure kodika

  ston pinaka kata tin diarkeia kataskeueis tou bazo mono osa bind simetexoun amesa i emesa
  se kapio filtro,alios ta bazo sto telos

5)tin sinartisi bind mporo na tin do san mia relation pou otan exo oles tis metablites tis
  bazo to neo node

  gia na ipologiso thelo na exo oles tis metablites apo tis relation queries
  kai meta efarmozo me tin sira tis opies bind metablites exo

  se 1 tree ta binds mpenoun me tin seira
  san pipeline
  px arxiki variable initialialPrice,travelCost

  (:= ?taxesPrice (* ?initialPrice (taxes ?zipcode)) )
  (:= ?shippingPrice (+ ?taxesPrice (shippingCost ?zipcode)))
  (:= ?finalPrice (+ ?shippingPrice ?paymentType))

  Ean sto project thelo mono to ?finalPrice tote to pano ginete

  (?finalPrice (+ (+ (* ?initialPrice (taxes ?zipcode)) (shippingCost ?zipcode)) ?paymentType))


